      es: "Un regalo bonito que contiene un\nregalo desconocido.\n\nPuede contener objetos exclusivos de\nNavidad 2015. Usa para abrir.",
      ja: "A fancy looking present which contains\nan unknown reward.\n\nMay contain exclusive items for Xmas\n2015. Use to open.",
      tw: "\u88DD\u8457\u795E\u7955\u734E\u52F5\u7684\u7CBE\u7F8E\u79AE\u7269.\n\u53EF\u80FD\u542B\u67092015\u8056\u8A95\u7BC0\u7368\u5BB6\u7269\u54C1.\n\n\u4F7F\u7528\u5F8C\u958B\u555F."
