  "1045": {
    name: {
      en: "Premium Super Lure",
      cn: "\u7CBE\u54C1\u767D\u94F6\u9999\u6C34(Premium Super Lure)",
      de: "Premium Superk\xF6der",
      fr: "Super Leurre Premium",
      it: "Super Aroma Premium",
      es: "Super Se\xF1uelo Premium",
      ja: "Premium Super Lure",
      tw: "\u7CBE\u54C1\u767D\u9280\u9999\u6C34(Premium Super Lure)"
    },
    description: {
      en: "A premium lure which attracts wild\nPok\xE9mon for 300 steps. It has several\neffects while active:\n\n- +25% encounter rates\n- Foes are stronger than normal\nencounters in the area\n- You may encounter more foes at the\nsame time\n- 10% chance to encounter lure-exclus\nive species\n- Small hordes (3) may increase in\nsize\n- If you encounter a Shiny Pok\xE9mon,\n'Secret Shiny' rates are increased by\n+25%\n\nConsumed upon use.",
      cn: "300\u6B65\u5185\u5438\u5F15Pok\xE9mon. \u6FC0\u6D3B\u65F6\u7684\u6548\u679C:\n\n- \u906D\u9047\u7387\u63D0\u534725%\n- \u91CE\u602A\u4F1A\u6BD4\u666E\u901APok\xE9mon\u7A0D\u5F3A\n- \u5355\u6B21\u9047\u602A\u4F1A\u66F4\u591A\n- 10%\u7684\u51E0\u7387\u5237\u5230\u4EC5\u9999\u6C34\u53EF\u9047\u7684\u7CBE\u7075\n- 3\u7FA4\u602A\u7684\u7FA4\u4F53\u6570\u91CF\u4F1A\u58EE\u5927\n- \u51FA\u95EA\u65F6, \u65B9\u5757\u95EA\u51E0\u7387\u63D0\u534725%\n\n\u4E00\u6B21\u6027\u6D88\u8017\u54C1.",
      de: "Ein Premium-K\xF6der, der wilde Pok\xE9mon\nf\xFCr 300 Schritte anlockt. Er hat\nmehrere Effekte, wenn er aktiv ist:\n\n- +25% mehr Begegnungen\n- Feinde sind st\xE4rker als normale\nBegegnungen in dem Gebiet\n- Du kannst mehr Feinde zur gleichen\nZeit treffen\n- 10% Chance K\xF6derexklusive Arten\nanzutreffen\n- Kleine Horden (3) k\xF6nnen an Gr\xF6\xDFe\nzunehmen\n- Wenn du einen Shiny Pok\xE9mon triffst,\nist die Chance auf ein 'Secret Shiny'\num +25% erh\xF6ht\n\nVerbraucht sich bei Gebrauch.",
      fr: "Un leurre qui attire les Pok\xE9mon\nsauvages pendant 300 pas. Il a\nplusieurs effets lorsqu'il est\nactif :\n\n- Taux de rencontre augment\xE9 de +25%\n- Les ennemis sont plus forts que la\nnormale\n- Vous pouvez rencontrer plus\nd'ennemis \xE0 la fois\n- 10% de chance de rencontrer des\nesp\xE8ces exclusives aux leurres\n\nConsomm\xE9 lors de l'utilisation.\n- Les petites hordes (3) peuvent\naugmenter en taille\n- Si vous rencontrez un Shiny Pok\xE9mon,\nles taux de 'Secret Shiny' sont\naugment\xE9s de +25%\n\nConsomm\xE9s lors de l'utilisation.",
      it: "Un aroma premium che attrae Pok\xE9mon\nselvatici per 300 passi. Ha diversi\neffetti durante l'attivazione:\n\n- Probabilit\xE0 di incontri +25%\n- Gli avversari sono un po pi\xF9 forti\ndel solito\n- Puoi incontrare pi\xF9 avversari\ncontemporaneamente\n- 10% di possibilit\xE0 di incontrare\nspecie attratte dall'aroma\n\n- Piccole orde (3) possono aumentare\nin dimensioni\n- Se incontri un Pok\xE9mon Cromatico, le\nchance di incontrare 'Cromatici\nSegreti' aumentano del 25%\n\nConsumato dopo l'utilizzo.",
      es: "Un se\xF1uelo premium que atrae Pok\xE9mon\nsalvajes durante 300 pasos. Tiene\nvarios efectos mientras est\xE1 activo:\n\n- Las probabilidades de encuentro\nsalvaje aumentan un 25%\n- Los enemigos son algo m\xE1s fuertes\nque los encuentros habituales\n- Es posible que te encuentres con m\xE1s\nenemigos a la vez\n- Aumenta en un 10% la probabilidad de\nencontrar especies exclusivas a\nse\xF1uelos\n- Las hordas peque\xF1as (3) pueden\naumentar de tama\xF1o\n- Si encuentras un Pok\xE9mon variocolor,\nla probabilidad de 'Variocolor\nSecreto' aumentan un 25 %\n\nSe consume al usarlo.",
      ja: "A premium lure which attracts wild\n\u30DD\u30B1\u30E2\u30F3 for 300 steps. It has several\neffects while active:\n\n- +25% encounter rates\n- Foes are stronger than normal\nencounters in the area\n- You may encounter more foes at the\nsame time\n- 10% chance to encounter lure-exclus\nive species\n- Small hordes (3) may increase in\nsize\n- If you encounter a Shiny \u30DD\u30B1\u30E2\u30F3,\n'Secret Shiny' rates are increased by\n+25%\n\nConsumed upon use.",
      tw: "300\u6B65\u5167\u5438\u5F15Pok\xE9mon. \u555F\u7528\u6642\u7684\u6548\u679C:\n\n- \u906D\u9047\u7387\u63D0\u534725%\n- \u91CE\u602A\u6703\u6BD4\u666E\u901APok\xE9mon\u7A0D\u5F37\n- \u55AE\u6B21\u9047\u602A\u6703\u66F4\u591A\n- 10%\u7684\u6A5F\u7387\u5237\u5230\u50C5\u9999\u6C34\u53EF\u9047\u7684\u7CBE\u9748\n- 3\u7FA4\u602A\u7684\u7FA4\u9AD4\u6578\u91CF\u6703\u58EF\u5927\n- \u51FA\u9583\u6642, \u65B9\u584A\u9583\u6A5F\u7387\u63D0\u534725%\n\n\u4E00\u6B21\u6027\u6D88\u8017\u54C1."
    }
  },
