  "1404": {
    name: {
      en: "Item Magnet Charm (+50%)",
      cn: "\u5BFB\u5B9D\u62A4\u7B26(Item Magnet Charm) (+50%)",
      de: "Item Magnet Charme (+50%)",
      fr: "Charme D'objet-aimant (+50%)",
      it: "Amuleto Magnete di Oggetti (+50%)",
      es: "Amuleto Im\xE1n (+50%)",
      ja: "Item Magnet Charm (+50%)",
      tw: "\u5C0B\u5BF6\u8B77\u7B26(Item Magnet Charm) (+50%)"
    },
    description: {
      en: "A charm which increases chances to\nfind items in wild battles. It\nincreases the chance of a Pok\xE9mon\nholding an item and the rate at which\nitems are randomly found.\n\nStacks with other bonuses.\nConsumed upon use.\nEffects last 1 hour.\nLink members receive a 10% bonus.",
      cn: "\u63D0\u5347\u5728\u91CE\u5916\u5BF9\u6218\u4E2D\u53D1\u73B0\u9053\u5177\u7684\u51E0\u7387\u7684\u62A4\u7B26. \u63D0\u5347Pok\xE9mon\u643A\u5E26\u9053\u5177\u4EE5\u53CA\u9053\u5177\n\u968F\u673A\u6389\u843D\u7684\u51E0\u7387.\n\n\u4E0E\u5176\u4ED6\u52A0\u6210\u76F8\u53E0\u52A0.\n\u4E00\u6B21\u6027\u6D88\u8017\u54C1.\n\u6709\u6548\u671F1\u5C0F\u65F6.\n\u5C0F\u961F\u6210\u5458\u989D\u5916\u6536\u76CA10%.",
      de: "Ein Amulett, das die Chance erh\xF6ht,\nGegenst\xE4nde in wilden Begegnungen zu\nfinden. Es steigert die Wahrscheinli\nchkeit, dass ein Pok\xE9mon einen\nGegenstand tr\xE4gt und die Rate, mit\nder zuf\xE4llig Gegenst\xE4nde gefunden\nwerden.\n\nStapelt sich mit anderen Boni.\nVerbraucht sich bei Benutzung.\nWirkung h\xE4lt 1 Stunde an.\nLink-Mitglieder erhalten einen Bonus\nvon 10%.",
      fr: "Un charme qui augmente les chances de\ntrouver des objets dans les combats\nsauvages. Il augmente les chances\nqu'un Pok\xE9mon tienne un objet et les\nchances de trouver des objets au\nhasard.\n\nSe cumule avec d'autres bonus.\nConsomm\xE9 lors de l'utilisation..\nL'effet dure 1 heure.\nLes membres du lien re\xE7oivent un bonus\nde 10%.",
      it: "Un amuleto che incrementa la\npossibilit\xE0 di trovare un oggetto\nnegli incontri selvatici. Aumenta la\nprobabilit\xE0 che un Pok\xE9mon tenga un\noggetto e il tasso con cui gli\noggetti vengono trovati casualmente.\n\nCumulativo con altri Bonus.\nSi consuma dopo l'utilizzo.\nL'effetto dura 1 ora.\nI membri Link ricevono un bonus del\n10%.",
      es: "Un amuleto que aumenta posibilidades\nde encontrar objetos en batallas\nsalvajes. Aumenta probabilidades de\nque Pok\xE9mon tengan objetos y la\nvelocidad de encontrar objetos al\nazar.\n\nSe acumula con otros bonos.\nSe consume al usarlo.\nLos efectos duran 1 hora.\nLos miembros del Link reciben un bono\nde 10 %.",
      ja: "A charm which increases chances to\nfind items in wild battles. It\nincreases the chance of a \u30DD\u30B1\u30E2\u30F3\nholding an item and the rate at which\nitems are randomly found.\n\nStacks with other bonuses.\nConsumed upon use.\nEffects last 1 hour.\nLink members receive a 10% bonus.",
      tw: "\u63D0\u5347\u5728\u91CE\u5916\u5C0D\u6230\u4E2D\u767C\u73FE\u9053\u5177\u7684\u6A5F\u7387\u7684\u8B77\u7B26. \u63D0\u5347Pok\xE9mon\u651C\u5E36\u9053\u5177\u4EE5\u53CA\u9053\u5177\n\u96A8\u6A5F\u6389\u843D\u7684\u6A5F\u7387.\n\n\u8207\u5176\u4ED6\u52A0\u6210\u76F8\u758A\u52A0.\n\u4E00\u6B21\u6027\u6D88\u8017\u54C1.\n\u6709\u6548\u671F1\u5C0F\u6642.\n\u5C0F\u968A\u6210\u54E1\u984D\u5916\u6536\u76CA10%."
    }
  },
