      cn: "\u88C5\u7740\u795E\u79D8\u5956\u52B1\u7684\u60CA\u609A\u793C\u888B.\n\u53EF\u80FD\u542B\u67092023\u4E07\u5723\u8282\u72EC\u5BB6\u7269\u54C1.\n\n\u4F7F\u7528\u540E\u6253\u5F00.",
      de: "Eine gruselig aussehende Geschenkt\xFCte,\ndie eine unbekannte Belohnung\nenth\xE4lt. Kann exklusive Gegenst\xE4nde\nf\xFCr Halloween 2023 enthalten. Zum\n\xD6ffnen verwenden.",
      fr: "Une pochette de cadeaux effrayante qui\ncontient une r\xE9compense inconnue.\n\nPeut contenir des objets exclusifs \xE0\nHalloween 2023.\nUtiliser pour ouvrir.",
      it: "Una busta regalo dall'aspetto\nspaventoso che contiene una\nricompensa sconosciuta.\n\nPotrebbe contenere oggetti esclusivi\ndi Halloween 2023. Usa per aprirla.",
      es: "Una bolsita espantosa que contiene un\nregalo desconocido.\n\nPuede contener objetos exclusivos de\nHalloween 2023.\n\nUsa para abrir.",
      ja: "A scary looking goodie bag which\ncontains an unknown reward.\n\nMay contain exclusive items for\nHalloween 2023. Use to open.",
      tw: "\u88DD\u8457\u795E\u7955\u734E\u52F5\u7684\u9A5A\u609A\u79AE\u888B.\n\u53EF\u80FD\u542B\u67092023\u842C\u8056\u7BC0\u7368\u5BB6\u7269\u54C1.\n\n\u4F7F\u7528\u5F8C\u958B\u555F."
