      cn: "\u53EF\u4EE5\u4FEE\u6B63\u67D0\u4E9BPok\xE9mon1\u70B9\u4E2A\u4F53\u503C\u7684\u7279\u6B8A\u5B9D\u73E0.\n\n\u4E00\u6B21\u6027\u6D88\u8017\u54C1.",
      de: "Ein besonderer Orb, mit der die IVs\nbestimmter Pok\xE9mon um 1.\n\nver\xE4ndert werden k\xF6nnen, wird bei\nGebrauch verbraucht.",
      fr: "Un orbe sp\xE9cial qui peut \xEAtre utilis\xE9\npour modifier les IVs de certains\nPok\xE9mon de 1.\n\nConsomm\xE9 lors de son utilisation.",
      it: "Una sfera speciale che pu\xF2 essere\nusata per alterare gli IV di certi\nPok\xE9mon di 1.\n\nConsumata dopo l'utilizzo.",
      es: "Un orbe especial que puede ser usado\npara alterar los IVs de ciertos\nPok\xE9mon por 1.\n\nSe consume al ser usado.",
      ja: "A special orb which may be used to\nalter the IVs of certain \u30DD\u30B1\u30E2\u30F3 by 1.\n\nConsumed upon use.",
      tw: "\u53EF\u4EE5\u4FEE\u6B63\u67D0\u4E9BPok\xE9mon1\u9EDE\u500B\u9AD4\u503C\u7684\u7279\u6B8A\u5BF6\u73E0.\n\n\u4E00\u6B21\u6027\u6D88\u8017\u54C1."
