      cn: "\u643A\u5E26\u540E\uFF0C\u4F7F\u51FA\u6280\u80FD\u7ECF\u8FC7\u547D\u4E2D\u5224\u5B9A\u800C\u672A\u547D\u4E2D\u65F6\u53D1\u52A8\uFF0C\u643A\u5E26\u8005\u901F\u5EA6\u5927\u5E45\u63D0\u5347\u3002\u4E00\u51FB\u5FC5\u6740\u6280\u672A\u547D\u4E2D\u6216\u8005\u76EE\u6807\u5904\u4E8E\u534A\u5B89\u5168\u72B6\u6001\u65F6\u4E0D\u4F1A\u6FC0\u6D3B\u3002\u4E00\u6B21\u6027\u6D88\u8017\u54C1",
      de: "An item to be held by a Pok\xE9mon. If the holder misses with an attack due to its Accuracy, Speed will sharply increase. It doesn't activate if missing with an OHKO move or if the target is semi-invulnerable. Consumed upon use",
      fr: "An item to be held by a Pok\xE9mon. If the holder misses with an attack due to its Accuracy, Speed will sharply increase. It doesn't activate if missing with an OHKO move or if the target is semi-invulnerable. Consumed upon use",
      it: "An item to be held by a Pok\xE9mon. If the holder misses with an attack due to its Accuracy, Speed will sharply increase. It doesn't activate if missing with an OHKO move or if the target is semi-invulnerable. Consumed upon use",
      es: "An item to be held by a Pok\xE9mon. If the holder misses with an attack due to its Accuracy, Speed will sharply increase. It doesn't activate if missing with an OHKO move or if the target is semi-invulnerable. Consumed upon use",
      ja: "An item to be held by a Pok\xE9mon. If the holder misses with an attack due to its Accuracy, Speed will sharply increase. It doesn't activate if missing with an OHKO move or if the target is semi-invulnerable. Consumed upon use",
      tw: "An item to be held by a Pok\xE9mon. If the holder misses with an attack due to its Accuracy, Speed will sharply increase. It doesn't activate if missing with an OHKO move or if the target is semi-invulnerable. Consumed upon use"
