  "5009": {
    name: {
      en: "Repeat Ball",
      cn: "Repeat Ball",
      de: "Wiederball",
      fr: "Bis Ball",
      it: "Bis Ball",
      es: "Acopio Ball",
      ja: "\u30EA\u30D4\u30FC\u30C8\u30DC\u30FC\u30EB",
      tw: "Repeat Ball"
    },
    description: {
      en: "A Pok\xE9 Ball which grows in strength\nevery consecutive capture of a\nspecies of Pok\xE9mon. It powers up even\nwhen using a different type of Pok\xE9\nBall. Its power is reset to 1.0x if\nyou capture something else, or if you\ndon't capture anything for a few\ndays.",
      cn: "\u8FDE\u7EED\u6355\u83B7\u540C\u79CD\u65CF\u7684Pok\xE9mon\u65F6\u80FD\u4E0D\u65AD\u63D0\u5347\u6355\u83B7\u7387\u7684Pok\xE9 Ball.\n\u5373\u4FBF\u7528\u522B\u7684\u7C7B\u578B\u7684Pok\xE9 Ball\u4E5F\u80FD\u63D0\u5347. \u5982\u679C\u6355\u83B7\u4E86\u53E6\u4E00\u79CD\u65CF\u6216\u8005\u51E0\u5929\n\u5185\u6CA1\u6709\u6355\u83B7, \u6355\u83B7\u7387\u91CD\u7F6E\u4E3A x1.0",
      de: "Ein Pok\xE9ball, der mit jedem\naufeinanderfolgenden Fang einer Art\nvon Pok\xE9mon st\xE4rker wird. Er wird\nauch dann st\xE4rker, wenn du eine\nandere Art von Pok\xE9ball verwendest.\nSeine St\xE4rke wird auf 1,0x\nzur\xFCckgesetzt, wenn du etwas anderes\nf\xE4ngst oder wenn du einige Tage lang\nnichts f\xE4ngst.",
      fr: "Une Pok\xE9 Ball dont la puissance\naugmente \xE0 chaque capture cons\xE9cutive\nd'une esp\xE8ce de Pok\xE9mon. Sa puissance\naugmente m\xEAme si vous utilisez un\nautre type de Pok\xE9 Ball. Sa puissance\nest ramen\xE9e \xE0 1,0x si vous capturez\nquelque chose d'autre, ou si vous ne\ncapturez rien pendant quelques\njours.",
      it: "Una Pok\xE9 Ball la cui potenza aumenta a\nseconda delle catture consecutive di\nuna specie di Pok\xE9mon. Aumenta la\npotenza anche se utilizzi un altro\ntipo di Pok\xE9 Ball. Torna ad avere\nefficacia 1x se catturi un'altra\nspecie, o se non catturi nulla per\nalcuni giorni.",
      es: "Una Pok\xE9 Ball cuya fuerza aumenta en\nfunci\xF3n de las capturas consecutivas\nde una especie de Pok\xE9mon. Aumenta su\npoder incluso aunque se utilice otro\ntipo de Pok\xE9 Ball. Su poder vuelve a\nx1 si capturas otra especie, o no\ncapturas nada durante unos d\xEDas.",
      ja: "A \u30E2\u30F3\u30B9\u30BF\u30FC\u30DC\u30FC\u30EB which grows in strength\nevery consecutive capture of a\nspecies of \u30DD\u30B1\u30E2\u30F3. It powers up even\nwhen using a different type of\n\u30E2\u30F3\u30B9\u30BF\u30FC\u30DC\u30FC\u30EB. Its power is reset to 1.0x\nif you capture something else, or if\nyou don't capture anything for a few\ndays.",
      tw: "\u9023\u7E8C\u6355\u7372\u540C\u7A2E\u65CF\u7684Pok\xE9mon\u6642\u80FD\u4E0D\u65B7\u63D0\u5347\u6355\u7372\u7387\u7684Pok\xE9 Ball.\n\u5373\u4FBF\u7528\u5225\u7684\u578B\u5225\u7684Pok\xE9 Ball\u4E5F\u80FD\u63D0\u5347. \u5982\u679C\u6355\u7372\u4E86\u53E6\u4E00\u7A2E\u65CF\u6216\u8005\u5E7E\u5929\n\u5167\u6C92\u6709\u6355\u7372, \u6355\u7372\u7387\u91CD\u7F6E\u70BA x1.0"
    }
  },
