    description: {
      en: "An item to be held by a Pok\xE9mon.\nIt slightly reduces the foe's\nAccuracy.\n\nIf held by a Wobbuffet while breeding,\nit may help them produce a Wynaut\negg.",
      cn: "\u7ED9Pok\xE9mon\u643A\u5E26\u7684\u9053\u5177.\n\u80FD\u7A0D\u5FAE\u964D\u4F4E\u5BF9\u624B\u7684\u547D\u4E2D\u7387.\n\nWobbuffet\u751F\u86CB\u65F6\u643A\u5E26\u5C06\u5F97\u5230Wynaut\u7684\u86CB.",
      de: "Ein Gegenstand, der von einem Pok\xE9mon\ngehalten werden muss.\nEr reduziert die Genauigkeit des\nGegners leicht.\n\nWenn er von einem Woingenau w\xE4hrend\nder Zucht gehalten wird, kann er ihm\nhelfen, ein Isso Ei zu produzieren.",
      fr: "Un objet \xE0 faire tenir \xE0 un Pok\xE9mon.\nR\xE9duit l\xE9g\xE8rement la Pr\xE9cision de\nl'adversaire.\n\nSi tenu par un Qulbutok\xE9 lors de la\nreproduction, il peut l'aider \xE0\nproduire un \u0153uf de Ok\xE9ok\xE9.",
      it: "Strumento da far tenere a un Pok\xE9mon.\nRiduce la Precisione del nemico.\n\nSe tenuto da Wobbuffet durante\nl'allevamento, permetter\xE0 loro di\ngenerare un uovo di Wynaut.",
      es: "Objeto que debe llevar un Pok\xE9mon.\nReduce un poco la precisi\xF3n del\nenemigo.\n\nSi lo lleva un Wobbuffet al criar,\npuede ayudar a crear un huevo de\nWynaut.",
      ja: "An item to be held by a \u30DD\u30B1\u30E2\u30F3.\n\nIt slightly reduces\nthe foe's Accuracy.\n\nIf held by a \u30BD\u30FC\u30CA\u30F3\u30B9 while breeding,\nit may help them produce a \u30BD\u30FC\u30CA\u30CE egg.",
      tw: "\u7D66Pok\xE9mon\u651C\u5E36\u7684\u9053\u5177.\n\u80FD\u7A0D\u5FAE\u964D\u4F4E\u5C0D\u624B\u7684\u547D\u4E2D\u7387.\n\nWobbuffet\u751F\u86CB\u6642\u651C\u5E36\u5C07\u5F97\u5230Wynaut\u7684\u86CB."
    }
