      cn: "\u7ED9Pok\xE9mon\u643A\u5E26\u7684\u9053\u5177.\n\u4F7F\u7528\u62DB\u5F0F\u8FDB\u653B\u65F6, \u5A01\u529B\u63D0\u534730%, \u4F46\u6BCF\u6B21\u8FDB\u653B\u4F1A\u635F\u5931\u81EA\u8EABHP\u6700\u5927\u503C\n\u768410%.",
      de: "Ein Gegenstand, der von einem Pok\xE9mon\ngehalten werden kann..\nWenn man diesen Gegenstand h\xE4lt,\nerh\xF6ht sich die Kraft der Attacken im\nKampf um 30%, aber auf Kosten von 10%\nder maximalen KP des Angreifers pro\nRunde.",
      fr: "Un objet \xE0 faire tenir \xE0 un Pok\xE9mon.\nTenir cet objet augmente de 30% la\npuissance des capacit\xE9s, mais au co\xFBt\nde 10% des PV Max de l'utilisateur\npar tour.",
      it: "Strumento da far tenere a un Pok\xE9mon.\nAumenta la potenza delle mosse del\n30%, ma l'utilizzatore perde il 10%\ndei propri PS Massimi ad ogni turno.",
      es: "Objeto que debe llevar un Pok\xE9mon.\nAumenta la potencia de los movimientos\nun 30% durante el combate, pero con\nel coste del 10% de los M\xE1x.PS del\natacante cada turno.",
      ja: "An item to be held by a \u30DD\u30B1\u30E2\u30F3.\nHolding this item will increase\nthe power of moves by 30% when in\nbattle,\nbut at the cost of 10% of user's\nMaximum HP per-turn.",
      tw: "\u7D66Pok\xE9mon\u651C\u5E36\u7684\u9053\u5177.\n\u4F7F\u7528\u62DB\u5F0F\u9032\u653B\u6642, \u5A01\u529B\u63D0\u534730%, \u4F46\u6BCF\u6B21\u9032\u653B\u6703\u640D\u5931\u81EA\u8EABHP\u6700\u5927\u503C\n\u768410%."
