      es: "Objeto que debe llevar un Pok\xE9mon.\nAumenta la potencia de un movimiento\nun 20% por cada uso consecutivo,\nhasta un incremento m\xE1ximo de 100%.",
      ja: "An item to be held by a \u30DD\u30B1\u30E2\u30F3.\nIt boosts the power of a move by 20%\nfor each consecutive use,\nup to a maximum increase of 100%.",
      tw: "\u7D66Pok\xE9mon\u651C\u5E36\u7684\u9053\u5177.\n\u9023\u7E8C\u4F7F\u51FA\u76F8\u540C\u62DB\u5F0F\u6642, \u5A01\u529B\u5C31\u6703\u63D0\u534720%, \u6700\u9AD8100%."
