  "5318": {
    name: {
      en: "Rose Incense",
      cn: "Rose Incense",
      de: "Rosenrauch",
      fr: "Encens Fleur",
      it: "Rosaroma",
      es: "Inc. Floral",
      ja: "\u304A\u306F\u306A\u306E\u304A\u3053\u3046",
      tw: "Rose Incense"
    },
    description: {
      en: "An item to be held by a Pok\xE9mon.\nIt increases the power of Grass-type\nmoves by 20%.\n\nIf held by a Roselia or Roserade while\nbreeding, it may help them produce a\nBudew egg.",
      cn: "\u7ED9Pok\xE9mon\u643A\u5E26\u7684\u9053\u5177.\n\u8349\u7CFB\u6280\u80FD\u5A01\u529B\u63D0\u534720%.\n\nRoselia\u6216\u8005Roserade\u751F\u86CB\u65F6\u643A\u5E26, \u5C06\u5F97\u5230Budew\u7684\u86CB.",
      de: "Ein Gegenstand, der von einem Pok\xE9mon\ngetragen werden kann.\nEs erh\xF6ht die St\xE4rke von Pflanzenatta\ncken um 20%.\n\nWenn es von einem Roselia oder\nRoseradebei der Zucht gehalten wird,\nkann es vielleicht dabei helfen, ein\nKnospi Ei zu produzieren.",
      fr: "Un objet \xE0 faire tenir \xE0 un Pok\xE9mon.\nAugmente de 20% la puissance des\nattaques de type Plante.\n\nSi tenu par un Ros\xE9lia ou un Roserade\nlors de la reproduction, il peut les\naider \xE0 produire un \u0153uf de\nRozbouton.",
      it: "Strumento da far tenere a un Pok\xE9mon.\nPotenzia le mosse di tipo Erba del\n20%.\n\nSe tenuto da Roselia o Roserade\ndurante l'allevamento, permetter\xE0\nloro di generare un uovo di Budew.",
      es: "Objeto que puede llevar un Pok\xE9mon.\nAumenta la potencia de los movimientos\nde tipo Planta un 20%.\n\nSi la lleva un Roselia o un Roserade\nal criar, puede ayudar a crear un\nhuevo de Budew.",
      ja: "An item to be held by a \u30DD\u30B1\u30E2\u30F3.\nIt increases the power of\nGrass-type moves by 20%.\n\nIf held by a \u30ED\u30BC\u30EA\u30A2 or\n\u30ED\u30BA\u30EC\u30A4\u30C9 while breeding,\nit may help them produce a \u30B9\u30DC\u30DF\u30FC egg.",
      tw: "\u7D66Pok\xE9mon\u651C\u5E36\u7684\u9053\u5177.\n\u8349\u7CFB\u6280\u80FD\u5A01\u529B\u63D0\u534720%.\n\nRoselia\u6216\u8005Roserade\u751F\u86CB\u6642\u651C\u5E36, \u5C07\u5F97\u5230Budew\u7684\u86CB."
    }
  },
